benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoiceItems/{invoiceItemId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to invoice item

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios cover successful modification of custom fields with various header combinations.
Non-Existing Resource: Scenarios handle attempts to modify non-existent invoice items.
Invalid Payload: Tests include malformed JSON and unsupported fields in the request body.
Concurrency Issues: Idempotency and performance tests cover potential concurrency issues.
Server Error Handling: Scenarios simulate database unavailability and dependent service failures.
gaps: Partial Update: No explicit tests to ensure partial updates are rejected unless allowed.
Rate Limiting: No tests cover how the system handles multiple requests in a short time.
recommendations: Add tests to explicitly verify that partial updates are rejected unless explicitly supported.
Include rate limiting tests to ensure the system handles multiple requests in a short time appropriately.
